1. Install Pipeline Maven Integration Plugin to use maven with pipeline
2. Add your gitlab credentials to jenkins global credentials for checkout
3. Create jenkins pipeline job 
4. Install Gitlab API Plugin, Gitlab Hook Plugin, GitLab Plugin
5. Add webhook on push events on your gitlab account and select gitlab triggeres in jenkins job
6. Upload the pipeline script on gitlab or create the pipeline on jenkins 
7. Auto install maven 3.6.3 in jenkins global tool configuration and give it a name eg: maven3.6.3
8. configure your email in manage jenkins -> configure system -> Extended E-mail Notification
